name: "Haunted (And Hungry)" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Ink on cardstock with sticker collage, digital embellishments, and digital color.] I made a Halloween card when the granddaughter was here. She loves ghosts. (And so do I!) This particular ghost is a graduate of a prestigious law school...who died as part of a tragic fraternity prank! He's making the best of his afterlife, but he is a bit HUNGRY (so steer clear!) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
